Package: researchCohortAnonymiser
Type: Package
Title: Evagene Integration Example - Research Cohort Anonymiser
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Fetches an Evagene pedigree, strips direct identifiers (names,
    precise dates of birth, free-text notes), and emits a research-safe
    JSON bundle or creates a fresh anonymised pedigree on the account.
    Structural only - not HIPAA Safe-Harbor compliant.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.3.0)
Imports:
    httr2 (>= 1.0.0),
    jsonlite (>= 1.8.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.2.0)
